com.qualcomm.hardware.ams

Class AMSColorSensorImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • <any>
      • com.qualcomm.hardware.ams.AMSColorSensorImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AMSColorSensor

    public class AMSColorSensorImpl
extends <any>
implements AMSColorSensor
    AMSColorSensorImpl is used to support the AdaFruit color sensor: http://adafru.it/1334 https://www.adafruit.com/products/1334?&main_page=product_info&products_id=1334 https://github.com/adafruit/Adafruit_TCS34725 AMSColorSensorImpl also supports the Lynx color sensor. More generally, there is a family of color sensors from AMS which this could support http://ams.com/eng/Support/Demoboards/Light-Sensors/(show)/145298 Importantly, this implementation sits on top of I2cDeviceSyncSimple instead of I2cDevice
